CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 4, 1972, pg. 15 reads: "The David Petetts - New Hope Baptist Church, Braddock, was the scene of the late summer rites, which solemnized the wedding of Miss Carol Elizabeth Mebane, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Warren Mebane, and David Edmond Petett, son of the Rev. and Mrs. Weldon D. Petett. The nuptial ceremony was conducted by the groom's father, who is pastor of Nazarene Baptist Church.  The happy pair has established residence on McPherson Blvd. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom David Edmond Petett and bride Carol Elizabeth Mebane Petett wearing eyeglasses and lace trimmed gown and veil, cutting three tiered wedding cake with columns, in New Hope Baptist Church with wood paneling, mirror, and twisted crepe paper streamers, Braddock
